##Update Raspberry Pi Bootloader and Firmware


Image the SDCard with Raspberry Pi Imager:  
`flatpak run org.raspberrypi.rpi-imager`

select latest Raspberry Pi OS.

On the terminal, run the following:
sudo apt update && sudo apt full-upgrade -y
sudo rpi-update  &&  sudo reboot

login
Log back in:
sudo rpi-eeprom-update -d -a
sudo reboot
sudo raspi-config 


 Enable SSH 
